title: RANK
body: I have already played my provisional game and  I was awarded as a silver 2 . but I find  I got nothing now. I have to play my provisional game again?

replies.body:
Hi! Looking at your account, it looks like you've only played three games since the start of the new season. 

Ranked in League of Legends works around roughly yearly time periods called seasons - when one season completes and another starts, you are then unranked until you play another provisional series. 

The 2015 Season started on Jan 21st - so you'll need to complete another 7 games to get your new starting rank for 2015. You can check out [here](http://oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/riot-games/announcements/get-ready-2015-ranked-season) for more info on the new season.
you mean you didn't get silver ?
